tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE engagement_metrics (
   metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   viewer_id INT,
   video_id INT,
   engagement_level INT,
   timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ViewerEngagementMetrics (
    viewer_id INT,
    video_id INT,
    engagement_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp DATETIME
)

CREATE TABLE ViewerProfiles (
    viewer_id INT,
    viewer_name VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    country VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Videos (
    video_id INT,
    video_title VARCHAR(100),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    upload_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Comments (
    comment_id INT,
    video_id INT,
    viewer_id INT,
    comment_text TEXT,
    timestamp DATETIME
)

CREATE TABLE Ratings (
    rating_id INT,
    video_id INT,
    viewer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp DATETIME
)
